{"tid":903473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國務院發言人指港基本自由受損      促北京港府遵守承諾","createTime":"2018-11-15T14:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T14:53:35.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2db4adf5ae30c61345ae0f5e91e29b19a04e5fe","tid":903473,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181115/large/1542288079_a1d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181115%2Flarge%2F1542288079_a1d2.jpg&h=13a15f0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼美國國會發表報告批評北京干預香港，建議將中港視為同一個關稅區後，美國國務院發言人諾爾特（Heather Nauert）今日凌晨亦在Twitter發文，指美方越來越關注香港發生種種破壞基本自由的事件，促請北京及特區政府遵守一國兩制原則下的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n中國時事評論員林和立接受《蘋果》查詢表示，將香港併入內地關稅區是美國政界，包括總統特朗普的高層都曾經嚴肅討論，他認為港府不應忽視，特別是報告提及中國透過香港公司購買美國高科技，正中特朗普最敏感、對中國竊取美國高科技的指控，但他相信美方對港政策變動，視乎中美雙方能否在月底於阿根廷舉行的G20峰會達成協議。林亦指，中央近年對港政策越來越嚴苛，特首林鄭月娥上場後卻「百分百執行中央命令」，直言對港府向中央力陳利害不寄厚望。<br />\n<br />\n林更指出，習近平早前會見林鄭表明《基本法》23條立法「慢不得」，顯示相關工作已開始籌備，「立法之後顯示香港高度自治大插水，更加使美國或特朗普同高層，（認為）既然香港高度自治名存實亡，再冇理由優待香港」，甚至會取消《香港政策法》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181115/58918230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181115%2F58918230&d=ZM%2FYmqnHOnhqe5jVT8WB9bIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d6a7dd84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181115%2F58918230&h=1d1b311e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181115/58918230</a>"},{"pid":"8aa9df0330877fe7dd711fd3aceaab7cc5ea339e","tid":903473,"uid":7699,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:38:08.000Z","msg":"快啲取消關係法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊共享做中國人嘅榮譽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea97aa4faf8fda0f9dc6cd3f6af40a867cc00b67","tid":903473,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af484ce0e07c3777d082a6fc115e4e69808f977c","tid":903473,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"By action<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686eb0341fe9442020f1af01cb55c4387dc76c71","tid":903473,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:42:52.000Z","msg":"warning letter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2ce8a19415f8f367fcdfeb1100d71a5e2f8726","tid":903473,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我大支那喜容外國人指指點點"}]}